<span class="c-key">STEP 1</span>  <span class="c-str">発話者セグメント分割</span>
pyannote → speaker_A / speaker_B / speaker_C に分類

<span class="c-key">STEP 2</span>  <span class="c-str">スパース化（重要発話のみ抽出）</span>
